{"tid":172184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲屋企好嚴","createTime":"2017-03-25T18:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T03:45:05.000Z","uid":77141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f962897cc0201f19ab92c9d09fd121186fdb486d","tid":172184,"uid":77141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:10:05.000Z","msg":"每次唔返屋企食飯同遲返屋企<br />\n都屌哂鬼咁 通頂都係大時大節先一兩次<br />\n講真我成廿歲都仲管住哂<br />\n明白佢地擔心 但每次出去玩都玩得唔放<br />\n十點幾就打黎叫我返屋企<br />\n遲返又形住形住驚佢地鬧<br />\n<br />\n重點啲聚會通常都約係市中心<br />\n我住新界返屋企點都要一個鐘<br />\n通常散band都十一,二點<br />\n返到去都一點幾<br />\n之後實會話我群埋啲唔三唔四嘅人<br />\n唔洗讀書啦乜乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真我都想自由啲姐 <br />\n可唔可以唔好下下都管住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240edcf9609f8212bea29d1e456dad080e4d50ea","tid":172184,"uid":33109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"我過1點翻就會比人屌  都唔知驚乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb6465e1cfda44db01b36ee9c59ff42ca8588a3","tid":172184,"uid":6573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"仲係細個個時就會<br />\n依家唔返屋企成日連電話都唔打比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ccaa44c84254689588c4c75c62e90f7d8ac6814","tid":172184,"uid":77141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我過1點翻就會比人屌  都唔知驚乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地成日以為有好多飛仔<br />\n真心我個邊零晨人影都冇個<br />\n都唔知驚咩"},{"pid":"34f45c2be6c19df078850f4a31f11ea2610aa97a","tid":172184,"uid":77141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲係細個個時就會<br />\n依家唔返屋企成日連電話都唔打比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma